{
  "id": "6a27b98b6922304003365d9e",
  "title": "とろける公共",
  "created": 1780988301,
  "updated": 1780991119,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a27b98b6922304003365d9e",
      "text": "とろける公共",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988301,
      "updated": 1780988301
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27b96800000000001bbb8d",
      "text": " 昔造った私の[造語][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988301,
      "updated": 1780988310
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27bbaf000000000002ccc8",
      "text": "  略して「とろ公」",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988884,
      "updated": 1780988892
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27b97100000000001bbb8f",
      "text": "  確か、「[新しい公共]」が流行っていた時期で、それに対置したもの",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988310,
      "updated": 1780988906
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27b9d300000000001bbb90",
      "text": "  公私の[揚保]（アウフヘーベン）、みたいな理屈をこねていたが、実際には語感が面白くて言いたかっただけという気も",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988408,
      "updated": 1780991119
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27b96800000000001bbb8e",
      "text": "  今なら新しい意味を付与できるような気もする",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988301,
      "updated": 1780988484
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27bb48000000000002ccc7",
      "text": "   [善の幾何学]的な、とろける共同体主義、みたいな感じで……",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988781,
      "updated": 1780988812
    },
    {
      "id": "6a27ba1700000000001bbb91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780988476,
      "updated": 1780988476
    }
  ]
}